        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="section" style="text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white;">
            <h2>üéâ Congratulations!</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.8;">You've completed the comprehensive guide to Data Representation in Computer Systems! You now understand number systems, conversions, negative number representation, floating-point arithmetic (sign-exponent-mantissa), and character encoding.</p>
